    <div class="grid">
        <div class="grid-item">
            <img class="image-oval" alt="Pediatric.jpg" src="~/Images/Pediatric_updated.jpg" />
        </div>
        <div class="grid-item">
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <h1 class="small-text green" style="text-align: left; margin-bottom: 20px;">Discover a path to wellness that is uniquely yours.</h1>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="smaller-text text" style="text-align: left">Brio Wellness Center is a <b>woman-owned</b> clinic dedicated to offering top-tier chiropractic and wellness-focused services for individuals committed to their personal growth. Our focus lies in a holistic approach to health, blending natural remedies seamlessly into daily life.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p class="smaller-text text" style="text-align: left">What distinguishes us is our belief that chiropractic care transcends mere spinal treatment—it's about nurturing the complete individual. Your mindset, enriched. Your physical well-being, enhanced. Because true health comes from embracing your utmost potential, ensuring you live life to its fullest capacity.</p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <a target="_blank" class="green-button" href="https://briowellness.janeapp.com/"><div class="smaller-text">Learn More</div></a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
